---
import ParmeliaStack from './ParmeliaStack.astro';
---

<section id="hero" class="hero-section hero-dark dark-field">
  <svg class="hero-network-bg" viewBox="0 0 800 400" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <g class="hero-network-base">
      <path d="M100,100 L300,200 L500,100 L700,250" />
      <path d="M50,300 L250,150 L450,280 L750,120" />
      <path d="M150,50 L400,350 L650,200" />
      <path d="M300,200 L250,150" />
      <path d="M500,100 L450,280" />
      <path d="M400,350 L450,280" />
    </g>

    <path class="hero-network-packet packet-sky" d="M100,100 L300,200 L500,100 L700,250" />
    <path class="hero-network-packet packet-pink" d="M50,300 L250,150 L450,280 L750,120" />
    <path class="hero-network-packet packet-cream" d="M150,50 L400,350 L650,200" />

    <g class="hero-network-node" transform="translate(300 200)">
      <polygon points="0,-14 14,0 0,14 -14,0" fill="#121212" stroke="#A7D4DE" stroke-width="3" />
      <circle r="4" fill="#A7D4DE" />
    </g>
    <g class="hero-network-node" transform="translate(500 100)" style="animation-delay: .6s;">
      <polygon points="0,-14 14,0 0,14 -14,0" fill="#121212" stroke="#DEA6BC" stroke-width="3" />
      <circle r="4" fill="#DEA6BC" />
    </g>
    <g class="hero-network-node" transform="translate(650 200)" style="animation-delay: 1.1s;">
      <polygon points="0,-14 14,0 0,14 -14,0" fill="#121212" stroke="#DED9A6" stroke-width="3" />
      <circle r="4" fill="#DED9A6" />
    </g>
  </svg>

  <div class="landing-shell">
    <div class="copy-stack wide" data-reveal>
      <ParmeliaStack className="hero-logo-glow" />

      <div class="relative w-full">
        <h1 class="hero-title hero-title-light">
          Mueve dinero digital sin fricción.
        </h1>
      </div>

      <p class="section-copy">
        Parmelia hace que cobrar y pagar con stablecoins se sienta como mandar un mensaje, no como usar una wallet cripto.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a href="https://app.parmelia.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-parmelia hero-cta">
          Probar Parmelia
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="microcopy hero-proofline">
        <span>Sin descargar apps</span>
        <span class="proof-dot proof-dot-sky" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span>sin frases semilla</span>
        <span class="proof-dot proof-dot-pink" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span>sin complicaciones</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
